	<h1 class="title">在动力解决之前，无人机送货到家只是形象工程</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1741/small/1741.jpg?1435203015" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">高宇馨</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-25 08:05:20 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7731/medium/7731.jpg?1436692999" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="7731" data-title="《在动力解决之前，无人机送货到家只是形象工程》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/7731/medium/7731.jpg?1436692999" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/7731.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
